I was in the Dance Scene in Youngblood (first girl to come through the line :-) and I've been looking for this DVD FOREVER! I was told it wasn't on DVD,that I had to order the Movie only thru Itunes. Just as I was getting ready to order the Movie I saw this Double Movie with YOUNGBLOOD!
I could not believe it! So I am very happy that they finally put it on DVD and I can watch my 26 year old self dance 39 Years ago!!
